{"tid":1172273,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"仲讀緊書嘅你，真心要學好啲英文","createTime":"2019-05-26T10:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T16:13:11.000Z","uid":138834,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84b1619fbe4bdfbeef7e66548890386419a8d955","tid":1172273,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排我去水族館叫雞<br />\n咁啱撞到有俄妹，個樣又唔錯<br />\n已經心中記低房號，準備掃完依層冇更好發現就返轉頭搵佢<br />\n<br />\n咁掃完啦，冇特別驚喜就諗住返轉頭啦<br />\n點知咁啱見到個阿叔快我一步㩒左鐘<br />\n<br />\n心諗：仆街了，今日冇啖好笑<br />\n<br />\n阿叔見到條俄妹咁正，一開口就用廣東話問<br />\n<br />\n幾錢呀？<br />\n<br />\n做雞嘅俄妹當然唔會識廣東話啦<br />\n就回左呀叔一句<br />\n<br />\nhmm&hellip;sorry?<br />\n<br />\n呀叔聽到呆一呆，個樣似係組織緊啲英文單字諗緊點講<br />\n<br />\n定左格幾秒，呀叔最尾放棄左，留低句<br />\n<br />\n冇野啦<br />\n<br />\n就一去冇回頭<br />\n<br />\n然後我就順利入閘了<br />\n<br />\n所以話，就算你知道將來做硬低賤工種唔洗用英文都好<br />\n學啲英文係日常生活都便利好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4092307734142813bd41f1b0c1798a88936c1fb4","tid":1172273,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfed14cee66e935f8c16d088041a4d39c8115c8","tid":1172273,"uid":52793,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"水族館唔係海洋公園咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bbbb2a8faa682a30cca0bdf575680df62ba50a","tid":1172273,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cfed14cee66e935f8c16d088041a4d39c8115c8","tid":1172273,"uid":52793,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"水族館唔係海洋公園咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"你都唔識野嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd4d2adfa532d41c30d7bcde54aa4646aaf751c","tid":1172273,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45bb